#Pandora preview ... I've never seen the movie, buy #Disney did a nice job with this.  Some kinks to work out for sure.  But, I know nothing about the film, but could follow along with this.

Some observations.  The land is smaller than you might think.  It's gonna be CROWDED.  So be prepared to feel like a sardine.  But much shade and lots of places to sit outdoors.

#AvatarFlightofPassage is an AMAZING RIDE.  But, although I fit in fine, larger people do not and can't ride it.  Current number is 1 in 4 people are too big to ride it.  That goes for my #bodybuilder and #powerlifter friends as well who are not accustomed to thinking of themselves as obese.  The calve restraints on the simulator do not engage if you have large calves, (fat or muscled) even if you fit into other areas perfectly well.  So don't be mad if they take you out for being too "large" for the ride when you are fit as hell.  It's probably your calves.

#Na'viRiverJourney is simple.  Think "It's a Small World" only under black lights with a less obnoxious song.

Setting is total immersion an Disney did well with that.  Better than they have anywhere to tell the truth.  Especially at night it's magical.

The city of #zagreb grew out of two #medieval #settlements - the #koptol at the centre of which is the Zagreb #cathedral and #gradec at the centre of which is the #parish #church of st.mark. The cathedral is known to be one of the most monumental gothic sacral buildings southeast of the Alps. The #romanesque church bears the #coat of #arms of Zagreb and the #triune #kingdom of #croatia #slavonia and #dalmatia in the form of the colourfull roof tiles. The entire old town now is well manicured and a treat to the eye.
